sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User
    participant AGW as Agent Gateway
    participant OIDC as OIDC Provider

    User->>AGW: GET /auth/login
    AGW-->>User: 302 Redirect to /authorize<br/>(client_id, redirect_uri, scope=openid profile email)
    User->>OIDC: Login prompt
    OIDC-->>User: Credentials
    User->>OIDC: Submit credentials
    OIDC-->>AGW: 302 Callback with authorization code
    AGW->>OIDC: POST /token<br/>(code, client_secret)
    OIDC-->>AGW: Bearer JWT (access_token + id_token)
    AGW-->>User: Session created
    Note over AGW: Configured via EnterpriseAgentgatewayPolicy:<br/>traffic.jwtAuthentication<br/>Validates JWT signature via JWKS endpoint
